Cout  => Character output
<< => insertion operator 
cout << "Hello World"; {Print statement in C++} or printf("Hello");
Code : 
#include <iostream>
int main() {

    cout << "Hello, World!";

    return 0;
}
Here int main() is a function in c++ programme.


